This is co, a simple toy language.

=== Routines ===
   Source Codes -> 
   Lexical Analyser ->
   Tokens ->
   Parser ->
   Abstract Syntax Tree ->
   Bytecodes (Opcodes) ->
   Virtual Machine ->
   Running Program

=== Name Conventions ===
    use general name for internal use as possible as you can, maybe specilized name for external use
    - CO
        C Object Compiler

    - CNode
        Node For Language Constructor

    - CVal
        Value Container

    - Opcode
       opline: opcode op1 op2

=== Zen ===
    Everything changes.

== Compile/Install ===
    $ # install bison/flex first
    $ make
    $ make install
